Package: ivTerm
Type: Package
Title: An interactive and comprehensive graphic system for functional analysis of meta-omics data.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Xiaorui", "Dong", email = "xiaonui8@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Xiaorui Dong <xiaonui8@163.com>
Description: ivTerm is an R-shiny package with a user-friendly graphical interface 
    that enables users to inspect functional annotations, compare results across multiple 
    experiments, and download customized charts. It utilizes shiny to creates a interactive 
    user interface (UI) healping resarcher to further explore and interpret gene functional 
    analysis results. Combination terms data with genes data provides a full view, helping 
    reseacher gain acctionable insight.
